&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or GED equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt to the changing needs of the lab.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail

